{"tid":342060,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有時真係覺得自己連大雄都不如","createTime":"2017-07-31T10:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T11:42:46.000Z","uid":65017,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd62da762199dd1686cef7275243d0f0fe1a929","tid":342060,"uid":65017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"大雄雖然成績差 成日比人蝦 冇咩叻（除左射擊同玩花繩）又懦弱 但佢有一班朋友共同進退 仲有多啦a夢幫佢 最後都娶到女神靜香<br />\n大雄起碼識得表達對靜香既愛意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我女性朋友都唔多個 又冇樣擅長 近排幾個幾好既朋友都冇埋 個人又懦弱 做野又三分鐘熱度<br />\n真係好想有個多啦a夢幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能我自細就中意多啦a夢既原因就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c83f48ff2384da955a36a09fa3c283315d4642","tid":342060,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:02:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0547ccb6543a3e5aaa24e623f7312479747bc82","tid":342060,"uid":65017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢屋企中產來喎好過唔少人</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf30cb874b1dfe0c630f17a6d7ecb708339a9e10","tid":342060,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:06:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c583a2fec05d1fa117fff2b1a1aea923e8b0ac8","tid":342060,"uid":28328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"隻係無多啦A夢已經輸成條街啦<br />\n仲想比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb83ab2951b336869218541e0f16085bcb30fe38","tid":342060,"uid":65017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢只係讀書唔掂  都叫冇負擔  算人生贏家  你點會比得起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯其實佢算係人生贏家<br />\n但細個完全唔發覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" cla